Localization.Name: Stronger Together Poster
Localization.Description: A point of inspiration to those who seek asylum in Levski, this poster recreates the memorable mural that greets visitors to the remote asteroid base in Nyx. Painted by an unknown artist, it features two hands clasped in unity over the symbol of the People's Alliance and the stirring motto of the political activist group: "Stronger Together."
